<title>USA: APS Holding president, CEO Hoffman resigns.</title>
<headline>APS Holding president, CEO Hoffman resigns.</headline>
<dateline>HOUSTON 1997-03-04</dateline>
<text>
<p>APS Holding Corp Tuesday said Mark Hoffman has resigned as president and chief executive to assume a senior position with Corporate Express Inc.</p>
<p>APS said chairman Hubbard Howe, who preceded Hoffman as chief executive, will return to serve in that position while the board conducts the search for a permanent replacement, the company said.</p>
